news.title: anas
news.content:
In the news-details.component.scss file, we added some CSS classes to center the title and apply a similar design. The details-container is a flex container, and the title-container takes up the remaining space and centers the title using flex: 1 and text-align: center.

Adjust the CSS styles as per your requirement to achieve the desired appearance.

By making these changes, the title will be centered within the title-container with the same design as in the news.component.html.

Let me know if you have any further questions!
